description:
Ready to stop overpaying for tickets? From the Cowboys to the Cavaliers, from Taylor Swift to Fleetwood Mac, from the College Football Playoffs to Broadway: You can use SeatGeek to find tickets for every kind of event.

SeatGeek is a search engine that scours hundreds of ticket websites at once and shows you all the tickets in one place. Use it to save time & money the next time you want a sweet deal on concert tickets, sports tickets, and more.

FEATURES:

• Tickets from 100s of websites, all in one place
• Great deals on concerts, sports, comedy, and Broadway
• Sort deals from from best to worst using Deal Score™
• Browse hi-res interactive seating charts
• View photos from each section before you buy
• Explore hot events near you
• Track your favorite artists for alerts when they come to town
• Track upcoming events & easily keep an eye on ticket prices
• 100% free
